replies.body:
Being killed and not even being allowed to react isn't actually a fun mechanic.

This isn't ONLY a problem with assassins ({{champion:1}} {{champion:78}}) but they've traditionally been the worst offenders. ({{champion:107}} {{champion:7}} {{champion:238}} {{champion:91}} )

I don't think i'll ever really like assassains but I realize they fill an important role.  I just feel like they need to have an appropriate balance of high risk and reward and not all of them do. {{champion:7}}
